| Layer | Authority | CSS prefix |
|-------|-----------|------------|
| Design system | `packages/design-system/src/registries/token.registry.ts` | `--afenda-*` |
| shadcn bridge | `packages/design-system/src/css/afenda-design-system.css` | `--background`, `--primary`, `--border`, ‚Ä¶ |
