## 8. Image-led auth (brand panel)

- **Mode:** artifact-led ‚Äî full-bleed photograph/scene, not floating UI card
- **Text:** anchored on scrim; brand kicker loudest
- **Form column:** utility copy, cardless (frontend-skill Apps)
- **Reject:** 3D tilt, beam animations, glass pill soup, dashboard-in-a-card

## 9. Figma MCP workflow

1. `get_metadata` ‚Äî list pages/frames (`fileKey: 2ZNqNOxyNb5TwCTBIaMVPD`)
2. `get_design_context` ‚Äî per frame `nodeId` (convert `1-2` ‚Üí `1:2`)
3. `get_variable_defs` ‚Äî token alignment
4. Adapt to governed React + BEM ‚Äî do not paste raw Tailwind output

